nodes.text: This game was a Star Wars fighting game originally set to be released in 2005 for the Xbox console.

Its demo showed Darth Maul and Revenge of the Sith-era Anakin Skywalker as playable characters, and the Death Star II as a possible location. Gameplay would have involved Lightsaber dueling, with kicks, punches, flips, stabs, slow-motion sequences, and Force pushes.
